Just one word is enough for describing this: Awesome!

Personally, I'm a Blu-Ray guy, but I purchased this set for my baby brother who's read the books and I gave him the first two movies on DVD for his birthday. (I'm also giving him movies 3 and 4 with this for Christmas.) They don't have a Blu-Ray player where he lives, so it was still DVD for him. I was glad to find this set for a low-cost but very acceptable way to get him the rest of the movies.

Note that this set is just the movie discs. If you're a type (like me) that enjoys hours of bonus features, you'd better look elsewhere. If you just want the Harry Potter films and don't need high definition video, this is one of now several options to get the last four films. There's sets of all eight films, the movies individually, and sets of two of the films together. Pick which is right for you and enjoy this well-done fantasy film series.

This is already available  under Best of Warner Bros. 'Harry Potter' Years 5-7 part 2 (4 discs), plus parts 1-4 are also available at Target for just $9.99 for each set!

Since I had already bought all the rest of the Harry Potter movies one at a time, I was looking to buy the rest of them to complete the set.  Instead of buying them individually, I was able to find this set for less than I would have spent on one of the movies separately.  What a surprise!  I am very pleased with them.
